cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI 

The paper deals with the physical layer security of UAV-ground communication, which involves wireless communication and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves network security and optimization, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper proposes an algorithm to solve the optimization problem, which involves control theory and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a likely category. Finally, the paper uses iterative algorithms and optimization techniques, which are also used in machine learning, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category as well.
